Hi Rosemary,

Sure, all products must have SKU so it would show up in column "item_sku".

Hi Joel,

Yes, I entered the item code into the inventory field, and then I did a manual export and it seem to fix it. I just wanted to double check that there wasn't anywhere else the code needed to go.

Thanks,

Rosemary

full_threads.body:
Hello,


We had an item which is not populating the item code on the order export.


Item THMRE55X - E55 Rechargeable Charcoal
https://thermacellrepellents.com.au/product/e55-rechargeable-mosquito-repeller-charcoal/


I went into the back end and noted that the item code was missing from the inventory field. So I have added it in. Now it seems to be populating in the summary area like all the other products. (It was the only one missing prior to be entering the code)


Would this be the only field that needs to be fixed, to have the code populating in the order export file?


Thanks,
Rosemary
